## Debugging workflow

When fixing bugs: reproduce → root cause → fix → regression test → verify → commit.

| Action | Command |
|--------|---------|
| Run tests | `npm test` or `npm run test` |
| Lint | `npm run lint` |
| Type-check | `tsc --noEmit` or `npm run type-check` |
| E2E | `npx playwright test` |
| Commit | `fix(scope): [bug description]` then `test(scope): add regression for [bug]` |

Regression: unit/component in `*.test.tsx`; E2E in `e2e/tests/*.spec.ts`. Ensure test passes after fix.

## Checklist

- [ ] Security: no secrets in frontend env; httpOnly cookies; sanitize inputs; CSP/SRI.
- [ ] Env: `.env*` per environment; never commit secrets; CI secrets for prod.
- [ ] CI: lint, type-check, test, build; bundle-size; Lighthouse thresholds; Dependabot/Renovate.
- [ ] Source maps: enable for Sentry (hidden or full); upload in CI.
- [ ] Husky + lint-staged for pre-commit.
